## File Status Legend

| Status | Color | Definition | Action Taken |
|--------|-------|------------|--------------|
| **Ready** | ğŸŸ¢ Green | New files that will be uploaded | Upload to storage |
| **Existing** | ğŸ”µ Blue | Files already uploaded previously | Skip upload, show notification |
